Title: Authorizes the discontinuance of certain parklands in the town of Cortlandville, county of Cortland
Summary: Authorizes the discontinuance of certain parklands in the town of Cortlandville, county of Cortland for lease to Park Outdoor Advertising of New York, Inc. for the purpose of erecting, maintaining and operating an electronic sign.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the town of Cortlandville to discontinue the use of certain parklands
